info.smart_tools.smartactors.utils.ioc.strategy

Class StrategyPack

  • java.lang.Object
    • info.smart_tools.smartactors.utils.ioc.strategy.StrategyPack
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ActorSystemIOCStrategies, CheckpointResolutionStrategies, ConfigAccessActorIOCStrategies, ConversionIOCStrategies, ConversionToConstructorIOCStrategy, DriverRegistration, DriverResolutionStrategy, IObjectWrapperCreatingIOCStrategy, ResolutionRules, ResolutionStrategies, SameClassNoConversionIOCStrategy

    public abstract class StrategyPack
extends Object
    Group of GeneralStrategy's that may be used by an IoC container. Strategies should be defined in classes extending this one (in overridden setupStrategies() method). No instances of that classes should be created explicitly. Pack's may be tagged using StrategyGroup or StrategyGroups annotations.
